race.comment: ZALI ZOOM (2) finished well back at Geelong last time when a 14 length seventh (23.25) but scored four back at this track (22.69). Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Has ability and can bounce back. DINOSAUR (3) finished second (22.63) two back at Warrnambool but out of the placings last time when 7th there. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Has ability and can atone. MISSY HIGHLAND (1) is worth forgiving last start after finishing eighth (23.69) from Box 8 at this track over 390m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from five starts. Bold showing expected. MORNING MIST (7) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.
